thing and I don&#x27;t know how to get the default options back.</p><p>I would really appreciate if you knew the answer.</p><p>Wonderful work nonetheless. I love it so much!<br><br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:4481347,&quot;user_id&quot;:912015}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies" id="post-4481347"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden version="1.1" height="20" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden version="1.1" height="20" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/pipoya" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1hZ2UyL3VzZXIvOTEyMDE1LzEyMjg1ODgucG5n/25x25%23/ElHQpB.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/pipoya">Pipoya</a></span><span title="2021-09-05 19:24:12" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/4481347">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Thank you for your comment. I&#x27;m glad you like this asset.</p><p>To reset the color change information in the generator, there is a shortcut key: press Ctrl + R.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:4481533,&quot;user_id&quot;:4832668}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-4481533"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden version="1.1" height="20" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden version="1.1" height="20" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/charmmycolour" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzcxMDgxNzcucG5n/25x25%23/OLNIEx.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/charmmycolour">Charmmy</a></span><span title="2021-09-05 19:37:13" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/4481533">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_b