 have a shade of red, blue, 2 greens.&nbsp;I added 3 outfits, an ear, and a hat. I have 2 more hair styles as well (been working on making pixelated Priconne characters and made Hatsune and Rino hairstyles)&nbsp;And I added an alternate Bow. I don&#x27;t know if you would be interested in these additional assets to share Pipoya, but If you do I would be happy to pass them along.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:3086115,&quot;user_id&quot;:912015}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies" id="post-3086115"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden version="1.1" height="20" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden version="1.1" height="20" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/pipoya" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1hZ2UyL3VzZXIvOTEyMDE1LzEyMjg1ODgucG5n/25x25%23/ElHQpB.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/pipoya">Pipoya</a></span><span title="2021-04-20 08:13:57" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/3086115">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Wow, that&#x27;s great! Thank you! I&#x27;ve been wondering if it would be possible for everyone to make parts of this. I&#x27;m so glad you did it. Thanks for the suggestion too! I would love to do this. However, if you have a character as a model, and that character is very unique, I may not be able to share it. I searched for characters to model, and I don&#x27;t think there&#x27;s anything wrong with the hairstyle. I&#x27;m looking forward to it!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:3088202,&quot;user_id&quot;:2008005}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies" id="post-3088202"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden version="1.1" height="20" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fpipoya.itch.io%2Fpipoya-free-rpg-character-sprites-32x32&amp;intent=community" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden version="1.1" height="20" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/voidwalkerz" class="avata